(169, 28, 10, '/cap-nhat-ve-nha-khoa/khang-sinh-thuong-dung-trong-nha-khoa', '/uploads/2014/10/25/1a3dfec4ce189e4d573f9b276cca0c02.jpg', 'Kháng Sinh Thường Dùng Trong Nha Khoa', 'Những kháng sinh hay dùng trong nha khoa và các sản phẩm hiện có trên thị trường hiện nay là gì? Hiểu biết và lựa chọn thông minh để bảo vệ sức khỏe của chính bạn.', '<p style="text-align:justify">Đi&ecirc;̀u trị bằng kháng sinh là m&ocirc;̣t ph&acirc;̀n quan trọng trọng dược lý học đi&ecirc;̀u trị. l&acirc;̀n đ&acirc;̀u ti&ecirc;n được sử dụng vào giữa th&ecirc;́ kỷ 20 bằng m&ocirc;̣t dạng thu&ocirc;́c sulfa (1935), peniciline (1941), tetracycline (1948) và erythromycine (1952). Càng ngày với sự đa dạng của b&ecirc;̣nh t&acirc;̣t, vi&ecirc;̣c nghi&ecirc;n cứu và cải ti&ecirc;́n tạo ra các th&ecirc;́ h&ecirc;̣ kháng sinh mới ngày càng phát tri&ecirc;̉n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify"><em><strong>Đặc đi&ecirc;̉m của vi&ecirc;̣c dùng kháng sinh trong đi&ecirc;̀u trị các b&ecirc;̣nh nha khoa và mi&ecirc;̣ng</strong></em></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Vi&ecirc;̣c k&ecirc; kháng sinh dựa tr&ecirc;n kinh nghi&ecirc;̣m của bác sĩ (bác sĩ kh&ocirc;ng bi&ecirc;́t chính xác loại vi khu&acirc;̉n g&acirc;y ra nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng này do vi&ecirc;̣c nu&ocirc;i c&acirc;́y mủ và dịch kh&ocirc;ng được ti&ecirc;́n hành thường xuy&ecirc;n ). K&ecirc;́t hợp với vi&ecirc;̣c thăm khám l&acirc;m sàng, quy&ecirc;́t định đi&ecirc;̀u trị kháng sinh được đưa ra</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- K&ecirc; các kháng sinh ph&ocirc;̉ r&ocirc;̣ng là t&acirc;́t y&ecirc;́u. M&ocirc;̣t phạm vi lớn vi khu&acirc;̉n được c&ocirc; l&acirc;̣p khỏi khoang mi&ecirc;̣ng, tuy kh&ocirc;ng phải t&acirc;́t cả chúng đ&ecirc;̀u nguy hi&ecirc;̉m và li&ecirc;n quan tới nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n căn b&ecirc;̣nh. R&acirc;́t nhi&ecirc;̀u các chủng vi khu&acirc;̉n li&ecirc;n quan tới nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng răng mi&ecirc;̣ng (c&acirc;̀u khu&acirc;̉n, trực khu&acirc;̉n, xoắn khu&acirc;̉n, vi khu&acirc;̉n gram dương, gram &acirc;m...)</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- S&ocirc;́ lượng kháng sinh được k&ecirc; hạn ch&ecirc;́ (chỉ từ m&ocirc;̣t, hai hoặc ba loại kháng sinh). Th&ecirc;m vào đó, vi&ecirc;̣c k&ecirc; đơn chỉ trong khoảng thời gian ngắn từ 7-10 ngày.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Sự nhạy cảm của vi khu&acirc;̉n với kháng sinh ngày càng giảm trong khi đ&oacute; s&ocirc;́ lượng vi khu&acirc;̉n kháng kháng sinh ngày càng tăng l&ecirc;n đặc bi&ecirc;̣t là Porphyromoha và Prevotella và giảm đ&ocirc;́i với các kháng sinh như peniciline, macrolides, clindamycin.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Kháng sinh thường được k&ecirc; cùng với thu&ocirc;́c ch&ocirc;́ng vi&ecirc;m kh&ocirc;ng steroids, c&acirc;̀n chú ý tương tác giữa hai loại thu&ocirc;́c đ&ecirc;̉ tránh tác dụng kh&ocirc;ng mong mu&ocirc;́n</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong>Chỉ định khi đi&ecirc;̀u trị kháng sinh trong nha khoa</strong></p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng răng mi&ecirc;̣ng c&acirc;́p tính</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng kh&ocirc;ng do răng</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Dự phòng nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng khu trú</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify">- Dự phòng nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng tại ch&ocirc;̃, nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng toàn th&acirc;n trong ph&acirc;̃u thu&acirc;̣t trong mi&ecirc;̣ng.</p>\n\n<p style="text-align:justify"><strong><em>Các thu&ocirc;́c dùng đi&ecirc;̀u trị nhi&ecirc;̃m trùng do răng</em></strong></p>\n\n<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Kháng sinh</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Đường dùng</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Tác dụng phụ</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">T&ecirc;n thương mại</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Amoxicillin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;N&ocirc;n, bu&ocirc;̀n n&ocirc;n, phản ứng quá m&acirc;̃n</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/amoxil.html"><strong>Amoxil</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/trimox.html">Trimox</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/moxatag.html">Moxatag</a>,</strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cons/amoxicot.html"><strong>Amoxicot</strong></a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Amoxicillin-Clavulanic acid</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng/Ti&ecirc;m tĩnh mạch</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p>&nbsp;N&ocirc;n, bu&ocirc;̀n n&ocirc;n, phản ứng quá m&acirc;̃n, vi&ecirc;m mi&ecirc;̣ng candida</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p><a href="http://www.drugs.com/augmentin.html"><strong>Augmentin</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/augmentin-xr-extended-release-tablets.html">Augmentin XR</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/augmentin-es-600-suspension.html">Augmentin ES-600</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/amoclan-suspension.html">Amoclan</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Clindamycin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng/Ti&ecirc;m tĩnh mạch</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Vi&ecirc;m đại tràng giả mạc</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/cleocin.html"><strong>Cleocin</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/cleocin-pediatric-suspension.html">Cleocin Pediatric</a>,</strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/cleocin-hcl-oral-injection.html"><strong>Cleocin HCl</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/cleocin-phosphate-oral-injection.html">Cleocin Phosphate</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Azithromycin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">R&ocirc;́i loạn dạ dày ru&ocirc;̣t</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/zithromax.html"><strong>Zithromax</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/azithromycin-3-day-dose-pack.html">Azithromycin Dose Pack</a>, Z-Pak,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/zmax-suspension.html">Zmax</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Ciprofloxacin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">R&ocirc;́i loạn dạ dày ru&ocirc;̣t</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cipro.html">Cipro</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/cipro-i-v.html">Cipro I.V.</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/cipro-xr-extended-release-tablets.html">Cipro XR</a>, Cipro Cystitis Pack</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Metronidazole</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Chóng mặt, t&ecirc; bì các chi, h&ocirc;̣i chứng cai rượu</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/flagyl.html"><strong>Flagyl</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/metro.html"><strong>Metro</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cons/flagyl-i-v.html">Flagyl IV</a>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/flagyl-er-extended-release-tablets.html">Flagyl ER</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Gentamycin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng/Ti&ecirc;m bắp</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Đ&ocirc;̣c cho tai, th&acirc;̀n kinh</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/garamycin-solution.html"><strong>Garamycin</strong></a><strong>, Cidomycin, Septopal</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:128px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Peniciline</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:109px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">U&ocirc;́ng/Ti&ecirc;m bắp</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:148px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Phản ứng quá m&acirc;̃n</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:254px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/pro/penicillin-vk.html"><strong>Penicillin VK</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/bicillin-l-a-suspension.html">Bicillin L-A</a>,</strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/veetids.html"><strong>Veetids</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/pc-pen-vk.html"><strong>PC Pen VK</strong></a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong><em>Các thu&ocirc;́c kháng sinh dự phòng vi&ecirc;m n&ocirc;̣i t&acirc;m mạc nhi&ecirc;̃m khu&acirc;̉n khi ti&ecirc;́n hành các thủ thu&acirc;̣t nha khoa</em></strong></p>\n\n<table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Kháng sinh</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Chỉ định</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Thời gian</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">T&ecirc;n thương mại</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Amoxicillin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Theo ti&ecirc;u chu&acirc;̉n</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;Trước 1h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p>&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Ampicillin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">N&ecirc;́u như kh&ocirc;ng dùng đường u&ocirc;́ng được</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Trước 1/2h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;<strong>Omnipen, Totacillin-N, </strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/principen.html"><strong>Principen</strong></a><strong>, Omnipen-N</strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Clindamycin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Dị ứng với penicillin và kh&ocirc;ng dùng đường u&ocirc;́ng được.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Trước 1h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Cephalexin/Cefadroxil</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Dị ứng với penicillin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Trước 1h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><strong>Cephalexin : </strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/keflex.html"><strong>Keflex</strong></a><strong>, Zartan, Keftab,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cons/bio-cef.html">Biocef</a> </strong></p>\n\n			<p style="text-align:center"><strong>Cefadroxil : </strong><a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/duricef.html"><strong>Duricef</strong></a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Azithromycin/Clarythromycin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Dị ứng với penicillin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Trước 1h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Clarythromycin : <a href="http://www.drugs.com/biaxin.html"><strong>Biaxin</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/cdi/biaxin-xl-extended-release-tablets.html">Biaxin XL</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style="width:151px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Cefezolin</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:205px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Dị ứng với penicillin và kh&ocirc;ng dùng đường u&ocirc;́ng được</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:115px">\n			<p style="text-align:center">Trước 1/2h</p>\n			</td>\n			<td style="width:169px">\n			<p style="text-align:center"><a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/ancef-injection.html"><strong>Ancef</strong></a><strong>,&nbsp;<a href="http://www.drugs.com/mtm/kefzol-injection.html">Kefzol</a></strong></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style="text-align:right"><em><strong>_ Tổng hợp_&nbsp;</strong></em></p>\n', NULL, 257, '2014-10-25 22:29:29', NULL, 0),
